cify is a descendant of the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIControl"},{"type":"text","text":" class, the map view calls this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"method as a convenience whenever the user taps your view. You can use this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"method to respond to taps and perform any actions associated with that control."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"For example, if your control displays additional information about the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"annotation, you could use this method to present a modal panel with that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If your custom accessory views are not descendants of the ","type":"text"},{"code":"UIControl","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" class,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the map view does not call this method. If the annotation has a custom callout","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"view via the ","type":"text"},{"code":"-mapView:calloutViewForAnnotation:","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" method, you can specify the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"custom accessory views using the ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNCalloutView","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"leftAccessoryView"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"rightAccessoryView"},{"type":"text","text":" properties."}]},{"anchor":"Related-examples","type":"heading","level":4,"text":"Related examples"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"TODO: Default callout usage, learn how to trigger an action when the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"standard callout bubble’s accessory control is tapped."}]}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[[